-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Menambahkan password di Windows 10 Home agar:
 	>>	Folder sharing minta password saat diakses dari PC lain
	>>	PC tetap auto-login (tidak minta password windows saat dinyalakan)
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Tujuan: "Folder Sharing Pakai Password"

	>> Tambah password akun lokal:
Settings → Accounts → Sign-in options → Password → Add
Buat password dan password hint

	>> Aktifkan "Password Protected Sharing":
Control Panel → Network and Sharing Center → Advanced Sharing Settings
Pilih: Turn on password protected sharing

Aktifkan Auto-Login supaya tidak diminta password windows saat booting:
Tekan Windows + R → ketik netplwiz
Hilangkan centang: Users must enter a username and password to use this computer
Masukkan username + password saat diminta → klik OK

(Opsional) Cek kembali hak akses folder share:
Klik kanan folder → Properties → Sharing & Security tab
Pastikan grup Everyone ada dan diizinkan (read/write sesuai kebutuhan)

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Menghapus password sharing di Windows 10 Home
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Tujuan: "Akses Folder Tanpa Password dari PC Lain"
	
	>> Matikan "Password Protected Sharing":
Control Panel → Network and Sharing Center → Advanced sharing settings
Pilih: ✅ Turn off password protected sharing
Klik Save changes

	>> Pastikan folder yang dibagikan diizinkan untuk semua orang:
Klik kanan folder → Properties → tab Sharing → Advanced Sharing
Klik Permissions → Tambahkan Everyone → beri centang Read (atau Full Control jika perlu)

Cek juga di tab Security:
Klik kanan folder → Properties → Security
Pastikan grup Everyone ada dan diizinkan akses


